            <p class="mb-6 text-base leading-relaxed text-[var(--color-ink-muted)]">
              <code class="inline-code">.deepdoc.yaml</code> lives in your repo root.
              <code class="inline-code">deepdoc init</code> writes sensible defaults; you only need to set
              <code class="inline-code">llm.provider</code> and your API key env var.
            </p>

